item.description:
Hey all,

It's time do to some karaoke! Castaways has karaoke every Saturday night. It is a quaint little bar in Dover, NH. We can catch a bite to eat and have some drinks and best of rock it out on the microphone! For anyone that does not know me castaways is a small bar, so it should not be hard to find me! If you have any questions or would like to contact me, then just shoot me an email. I would be happy to answer any questions. Hope to see you there!
